comment: This is such a lovely "warm tone makeup for cool tones" tutorial, especially for the summer.  It is peach pink with the right balance, not too warm. Beryoung, please try the new Holika eyeshadow, they released new colors... Tulle and Rotallic would look so good with this makeup for aegyosal. And the lining shading shadow Dark Espresso is dark cool brown with no redness.
와 진짜 무슨 벚꽃요정인줄알았어요...웜쿨 평화를위한 메컵 너무좋네요!
블러셔 위치 영역 잡으신 게 흔하지 않은데 얼굴에 어울리고 예뻐요! 미지근한 색감 조합에 흑발 정말 상큼합니다
